0efdb546-971b-47de-ac35-51c209bcda7b.title: Estate agent
0efdb546-971b-47de-ac35-51c209bcda7b.text:
Hello. Welcome to the Gielinor Housing Agency! What
can I do for you?

options.text: How can I get a house?

c4e0d917-bd8c-4415-98d9-6c2a7d519d76.title: Estate agent
c4e0d917-bd8c-4415-98d9-6c2a7d519d76.text:
It all came out of the wizards' experiments. They found
a way to fold space, so that they could pack many acres
of land into an area only a foot across.

45e92fdf-e261-488a-b0ca-4f49df990b32.title: Estate agent
45e92fdf-e261-488a-b0ca-4f49df990b32.text:
They created several folded-space regions across"
Gielinor. Each one contains hundreds of small plots
where people can build houses.

2d9b6413-710c-4810-8477-4814a25a6075.title: <player>
2d9b6413-710c-4810-8477-4814a25a6075.text:
Ah, so that's how everyone can have a house without
them cluttering up the world!

9253322e-a23b-44c5-bc7f-733e6e1f5b61.title: Estate agent
9253322e-a23b-44c5-bc7f-733e6e1f5b61.text:
Quite. The wizards didn't want to get bogged down in
the business side of things so they hired me to sell the
houses.

2ed9f34c-dd8f-438c-9bf7-8aae971af39f.title: Estate agent
2ed9f34c-dd8f-438c-9bf7-8aae971af39f.text:
There are various other people across Gielinor who can
help you furnish your house.

81495211-f10e-412c-836a-4040e3a444bc.title: Estate agent
81495211-f10e-412c-836a-4040e3a444bc.text:
You should start by buying planks from a sawmill
operator. Sawmills are located in north-east Varrock, the
Woodcutting Guild located in south-west Hosidius and
north-east Prifddinas.

bad97287-0fc1-43b0-ba24-996f162e560d.title: <player>
bad97287-0fc1-43b0-ba24-996f162e560d.text: How can I get a house?

73b4e77f-b72d-47c6-84ac-14d326124783.title: Estate agent
73b4e77f-b72d-47c6-84ac-14d326124783.text:
I can sell you a starting house in Rimmington for
1000 coins. As you increase your construction skill you
will be able to have your house moved to other areas
and redecorated in other styles.

a7c52c83-5e83-4b52-9a9f-fb1219ecf7ca.title: Estate agent
a7c52c83-5e83-4b52-9a9f-fb1219ecf7ca.text: Do you want to buy a starter house?

98426974-9e8e-4df9-b7c7-74e091a4703f.title: Estate agent
98426974-9e8e-4df9-b7c7-74e091a4703f.text:
Well enjoy your player-owned cardboard box or
wherever you're going to sleep tonight!

239b44e8-d616-48cf-b742-d1babf1f44ae.title: <player>
239b44e8-d616-48cf-b742-d1babf1f44ae.text: I haven't got 1,000 coins on me.

1fe389b5-539d-47fd-b870-d300b20d86fc.title: Estate agent
1fe389b5-539d-47fd-b870-d300b20d86fc.text: Well come back when you have it then.

7feb2d07-3463-46cd-b468-49fe97b27d30.title: Estate agent
7feb2d07-3463-46cd-b468-49fe97b27d30.text:
Thank you. Go through the Rimmington house portal
and you will find your house ready for you to start
building in it.

b7a31da6-35cc-4f73-bd61-be8f53a973f5.title: <player>
b7a31da6-35cc-4f73-bd61-be8f53a973f5.text: This book will help you to start building your house.

a1477683-cb4e-4204-8a58-84b775647109.title: Estate agent
a1477683-cb4e-4204-8a58-84b775647109.text:
Hello. Welcome to the Gielinor Housing Agency! What
can I do for you?

options.text: Can you move my house please?
Can you redecorate my house please?
Could I have a Construction guidebook?
Tell me about that skillcape you're wearing.

d5d44262-98cd-486e-8feb-0da8434b3123.title: Estate agent
d5d44262-98cd-486e-8feb-0da8434b3123.text:
It all came out of the wizards' experiments. They found
a way to fold space, so that they could pack many acres
of land into an area only a foot across.

34c1126a-a559-4873-9d62-a419cb00dc02.title: Estate agent
34c1126a-a559-4873-9d62-a419cb00dc02.text:
They created several folded-space regions across"
Gielinor. Each one contains hundreds of small plots
where people can build houses.

048f651f-8d80-41ed-8881-68c38d582cd8.title: <player>
048f651f-8d80-41ed-8881-68c38d582cd8.text:
Ah, so that's how everyone can have a house without
them cluttering up the world!

3db1f7d2-7eee-40ed-9625-874bfa5907f1.title: Estate agent
3db1f7d2-7eee-40ed-9625-874bfa5907f1.text:
Quite. The wizards didn't want to get bogged down in
the business side of things so they hired me to sell the
houses.

10876425-b9a8-4b42-9269-7fa2b27015f8.title: Estate agent
10876425-b9a8-4b42-9269-7fa2b27015f8.text:
There are various other people across Gielinor who can
help you furnish your house.

742c285a-e112-4954-8e2a-476e5ad413ad.title: Estate agent
742c285a-e112-4954-8e2a-476e5ad413ad.text:
You should start by buying planks from a sawmill
operator. Sawmills are located in north-east Varrock, the
Woodcutting Guild located in south-west Hosidius and
north-east Prifddinas.

e29842ab-0b71-4449-83a3-d528768a34f9.title: <player>
e29842ab-0b71-4449-83a3-d528768a34f9.text: Tell me about that skillcape you're wearing.

15ad86b3-62ea-43e8-b70f-cc608029ff02.title: Estate agent
15ad86b3-62ea-43e8-b70f-cc608029ff02.text:
As you may know, skillcapes are only available to
masters in a skill. I have spent my entire life building
houses and now I spend my time selling them! As a
sign of my abilities I wear this Skillcape of Construction.

935291dd-f087-4f61-a92e-0334298145ea.title: Estate agent
935291dd-f087-4f61-a92e-0334298145ea.text:
If you ever have enough skill to build a demonic throne,
come and talk to me and I'll sell you a skillcape like
mine.

18b6bf93-d888-4431-a397-4ffc653cedce.title: Estate agent
18b6bf93-d888-4431-a397-4ffc653cedce.text:
The Cape of Construction also provides you with as
many teleports as you like to any of the house portals
or even directly inside!

6b75974a-ca6e-4f8e-96f8-3aebb1e1ef3e.title: <player>
6b75974a-ca6e-4f8e-96f8-3aebb1e1ef3e.text: Could I have a Construction guide book?

0ea5906a-3082-4bdd-828b-6a905ef6252f.title: <player>
0ea5906a-3082-4bdd-828b-6a905ef6252f.text: Can you redecorate my house please?

e2df0f19-1084-4be4-9b73-2d5293f9e667.title: Estate agent
e2df0f19-1084-4be4-9b73-2d5293f9e667.text:
Certainly. My magic can rebuild the house in a
completely new style! What style would you like?

04744e50-6e56-4d8a-8f80-50ea98cfe88f.title: <player>
04744e50-6e56-4d8a-8f80-50ea98cfe88f.text: Can you move my house please?

ad5ee851-244e-4bd7-b52d-a17eb6619e05.title: Estate agent
ad5ee851-244e-4bd7-b52d-a17eb6619e05.text: Where would you like it moved to?
